{
  "stem": "20142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] How did we-- there was a certain amount of hope in us, especially when we heard the airplanes passing by and there was a raid.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we knew that there were Russian planes coming over on the-- on-- on the-- on the way to bombard something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was the only few minutes of rest that we really had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it came that the sleeping was permitted the minute the lights were out at 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At 4 o'clock in the morning, they get you-- got you out on a place to be counted and be prepared for the day shift to work on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Condition of living in the barracks were awful, and we had lice that were eating us alive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was no hope of being able to get rid of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Many people were sitting at night and just killing lice in their uniform, because they couldn't stand it anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And many with the lice of course came the typhus epidemic and decimated our ranks without any-- without any mercy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we went to work--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew very well that the only way to survive is to-- to support one another, extend the good word of-- of friendship.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no fighting among the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially when you encounter the hanging of a prisoner, and especially conducted on Sundays.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For what reason that they?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't matter what reason it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans declared this individual guilty, and they hung him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- we had to witness this, standing on appelplatz, after we returned from work after half a day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On Sunday, we were working half a day.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
